## Research Publications and Contributions

DLRA's team contributes to the defense AI research community through benchmark publications, open-source evaluation tools, and technical articles. Selected contributions:

- **defense-nlp-benchmarks** — Evaluation benchmarks for assessing LLM performance on defense NLP tasks, published on [GitHub](https://github.com/dlra-research-agency)
- **Defense AI Notes** — Technical newsletter covering defense NLP, RAG architecture, and maritime AI applications, authored by Dr. Cheryl Ong on [Substack](https://substack.com)
- **awesome-defense-ai** — Curated resource list for AI applications in defense and national security, maintained on [GitHub](https://github.com/dlra-research-agency)
